    <br><br /><br><br /><br><br /><br><br /><br><br /><br><br /><br>
    Now that we finally are defrosted from months of living under the snow, it&rsquo;s time to start planning all the wonderful ways to get outdoors again. One option is through a wine tour! Pair Wine Tours offers three New York City neighborhood wine tours with options located in Hell&rsquo;s Kitchen, The Lower East Side or Hoboken. Guests will visit two restaurants and one wine shop while enjoying delicious bites and learning everything you&rsquo;d ever wanted to know about wine from a hands-on sommelier!
